string.name: say
string.value: One foot in front of the other... Speed it up, pal.

string.name: say
string.value: You're all right, but I've seen better.

string.name: say
string.value: Heck yeah! I'm diggin' the beat.

string.name: say
string.value: Your turn. Persuade this guy to move.

string.name: say
string.value: Stick close. You can't handle this place without me.

string.name: say
string.value: We meet again. All right, follow me, you lost, pitiful soul.
